data.description: Your privacy awaits at this beautiful home with 3 acres. The entire home has been recently remodeled and the kitchen has gorgeous butcher block countertops. The primary bedroom has it's own private bathroom. The basement has been recently finished for some added enjoyment. Enjoy a book on your back deck overlooking your 3 acres.This home is cozy and waiting for the next family. The possibilities here are endless!
